[02:16.04]The version of me that I used to know
[02:21.68]Is standing at the door, but I won't let him go
[02:28.22]I keep him locked behind the person I became
[02:34.66]Afraid that letting him in means losing this game
[02:41.90]I'm falling into something I can't name
[02:47.70]A shadow wearing me, playing my game
[02:54.52]I don't recognise the eyes staring back
[03:00.66]I followed all my fears right off the track
